Package: ds4to360xboxdrv
Architecture: any
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, xboxdrv, python3-gi, libgtk-4-1, libadwaita-1-0, systemd, python3-evdev, python3-pyudev
Description: DualShock 4/3 and DualSense to Xbox 360 Controller Mapper
 ds4to360xboxdrv is a tool to emulate an Xbox 360 controller on Linux using
 DualShock 4, 3, or DualSense controllers. It features a modern GTK4/Libadwaita
 GUI and a robust backend using xboxdrv and evdev.
